6
00:00:17,310 --> 00:00:21,140
There are five reasons for doing experiments.

7
00:00:21,140 --> 00:00:24,590
The first is to document behavioral phenomena.

8
00:00:24,590 --> 00:00:29,460
Any major phenomena, like decision biases
or strategies used for making

9
00:00:29,460 --> 00:00:33,649
