10
00:00:33,649 --> 00:00:38,109
time that converge towards the same conclusion.

11
00:00:38,109 --> 00:00:43,059
Second, experiments are often run to develop
a theory to explain the

12
00:00:43,059 --> 00:00:46,769
phenomena that have been documented, as we
discussed earlier.

13
00:00:46,769 --> 00:00:51,379
Third, we often do experiments to study the
