behavior changing interventions.

24
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:35,450
So these are five good reasons for why experiments
are typically conducted.

25
00:01:35,450 --> 00:01:38,520
Every experiment studies the relationship
between one variable,

26
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:42,450
that we call a cause, and it's consequence,
which is

27
00:01:42,450 --> 00:01:44,420
often called an effect.

28
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:49,880
In a nutshell, every experiment tries to show
that a particular cause

29
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:53,560
results in a specific effect.

30
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:58,230
For example, framing a price as pennies a
day, or framing a request

31
00:01:58,230 --> 00:02:03,670
