55
00:03:44,450 --> 00:03:48,680
something as pennies a day increases in greater
spending.

56
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:52,590
But if you remember, this effect happens only
when the pennies a day

57
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:58,169
frame results in a dollar amount that can
be compared easily to other

58
00:03:58,169 --> 00:04:02,499
expenses that the consumer might make that
