65
00:04:28,340 --> 00:04:33,660
for small daily amounts and not when, in fact,
the daily amount or the daily

66
00:04:33,660 --> 00:04:36,600
equivalent is large.

67
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:41,310
In the language of experimental design, this
